From the contract description, we can see that this is an Interest Rate Cap and Floor Swap Contract. In a cap and floor swap, the counterparty that has the cap option (right to receive the higher of the two rates) is the receiver, and the counterparty that has the floor option (right to receive the lower of the two rates) is the payer.
